A hashed container abstraction.
Template Parameters
Key
Key type.
Mapped
Map type.
Hash_Fn
Hashing functor.
Eq_Fn
Equal functor.
Resize_Policy
Resizes hash.
Store_Hash
Indicates whether the hash value will be stored along with each key.
Tag
Instantiating data structure type, see container_tag.
Policy_TL
Policy typelist.
_Alloc
Allocator type.
Base is dispatched at compile time via Tag, from the following choices: cc_hash_tag, gp_hash_tag, and descendants of basic_hash_tag.
Base choices are: detail::cc_ht_map, detail::gp_ht_map
